so-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">魔芋纤维米</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体\">”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">晶莹剔透，酷似天然稻米，口感滑润充盈，富有弹性，蒸煮随意。具有润肠通便，降三高，减肥瘦身之功效。</SPAN></P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">\n<P style=\"WORD-BREAK: break-all; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">国外的一些营养学家曾做过这样一个试验，将小白鼠分成两组，投喂等量高脂肪食物，一组不加魔芋，另一组加少量魔芋粉，结果加喂魔芋的一组小白鼠体内胆固醇含量比另一组低</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt\">100</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">毫克以上。科学家认为，魔芋中含有一些化学物质，能降低血清胆固醇和甘油三酯，同时魔芋膳食纤维可以在肠道内吸附脂肪和胆固醇，并将其中一部分裹携，随粪便排除体外，减少人体对脂肪和胆固醇的吸收，可有效地减轻高血压和心血管疾病。</SPAN></P>\n<P style=\"WORD-BREAK: break-all; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">因为魔芋本身富含丰富的可溶性膳食纤维，当人体食进魔芋米以后会变成很粘稠的物质，这种粘稠物质一方面可以把营养物质包裹起来，阻止它快速的被小肠吸收，同时它也会在小肠壁形成一层很粘的物质来屏蔽，使营养吸收减慢。这样碳水化合物进入血液中的速度就减慢了，那么血糖的高峰、低谷就会拉平，这样的作用就叫血糖平衡作用。</SPAN></SPAN></P>\n<P style=\"WORD-BREAK: break-all; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </P></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><br>符合贵州省天龙魔芋食品有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
