INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('5073','长康因子（会议营销、肠胃、保健品、会议营销、心脑血管、会议营销、骨关节、糖尿病）招商 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的改善胃肠类招商信息：<br><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">\n<P class=Mso<em></em>normal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">随着神舟七号飞船再次使用水苏糖</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">STA</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">因子作为宇航员的主要饮品添加成分，长康因子的母体——水苏糖</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">STA</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">因子成为新闻媒体和老百姓所关注的对象。其实作为一种安全的微生态调节产品，水苏糖</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">STA</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">早已成为日本、欧美国家对抗慢性疾病、慢性炎症，调理胃肠功能，日常保健的常用产品。由日本东京大学微生物应用研究所提取的高纯度水苏糖</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">STA</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">因子分子式为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">c24h42o21</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">分子量为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">666.59</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">，不会被人体消化酶所水解，可完整地进入结肠，并被肠道益生菌所酵解，能显著促进双歧杆菌、乳酸杆菌等</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">100</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">多种有益菌增殖，是优良的有益菌活性增殖因子，被誉为“超级益生元”（简称</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">STA</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">）。因为是肠道众多益生菌所需要的营养素，水苏糖</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">STA</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">能直接对使用者的胃肠健康有益，并减轻多种胃肠道感染和不适（胃炎、肠炎、便秘），减少结肠癌、胃癌的发病率。水苏糖还可以防止蛀牙，治疗便秘，促进肠道吸收矿物质及改善骨骼的矿物质沉积。它还可以作为某些特殊人群的理想食品添加剂，例如糖尿病病人。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"> <BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">　　</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"> </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">会议营销市场中一直缺少拥有真正高科技含量，主攻方向是胃肠功能的好产品，长康因子的出现，为会销经营者提供了真正卖点好、有效果、无副作用（腹泻或便秘）的产品。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">本品采用日本东京大学附属应用微生物所专利技术从天然植物中提取的高纯度水苏糖为主要原料，经功能实验证明，本品可促进人体肠道内双歧杆菌、乳酸杆菌等有益菌的增殖，抑制致病菌的繁殖增长，具有改善胃肠道功能（调节肠道菌群）和免疫调节的保健作用。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">【批准文号】卫食健字（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">1998</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">）第</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">429</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">号</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">【主要原料】水苏糖</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">STA</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">因子</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">【功效成份及含量】水苏糖</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">STA</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">因子</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">45</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">—</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">50%<BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">【保健功能】改善胃肠道功能（调节肠道菌群）、免疫调节</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">【适宜人群】胃肠道功能紊乱、菌群失调、体质虚弱及免疫力低下者</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">【食用方法及食用量】餐后服用，每次两粒，早晚各一次，儿童酌减</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><BR></SPAN><SPAN