span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">母乳中就含有左旋肉碱，对人体无毒副作用。自从科学界发现左旋肉碱以来，就被推荐为科学的重要成分</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">!</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">人体内的左旋肉碱含量决定了人体的胖瘦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">左旋肉碱多，脂肪燃烧快，人就瘦，左旋肉碱少，脂肪燃烧慢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">人就胖</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">.</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">这就是有人大吃大喝也不胖，有人喝凉水也长胖的秘密所在，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">2003</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">年被国际肥胖健康组织认定为最安全无副作用的减肥营养补充品。</span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;background:#fafafa;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\">柑橘多酚：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">纯天然的水果提取物</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">结合现在科技生产的高效产品。主要成分为柑橘类水果萃取物（红柳橙、葡萄柚、柳橙）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">, 100