INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('5126','减肥李.酵素vc果 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的减肥丰胸类招商信息：<br><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">食用方法：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">一</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">日一次，晚餐后或睡前拆开一包嚼食</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">内有果核请勿吞食</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">食用人群：便秘、体内垃圾、毒素沉积排毒养颜者，应酬多暴饮暴食保持身材者</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">保质期限：18个月</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">保存方法：避免置于高温、潮湿及日光直射处，冷藏后口感更佳。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">注意事项：幼儿、孕妇不建议食用；严重消化道溃疡者慎用；</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">作用过程：燃脂梅全球首创“水果载体”&nbsp;专业解决女性“三排”（&nbsp;排便、排毒、排油）问题，&nbsp;快速清除体内垃圾的完美产品，排毒养颜者效果“加速机”&nbsp;，一天一粒，排出体内垃圾，由内而外从源头上彻底消灭“美丽杀手”！健康美丽。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;排便：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">小时滋润肠胃，通便排毒。燃脂梅中富含的乳酸菌、双歧因子在肠道迅速繁殖</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">兆活性有益菌</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">肠道壁上的肥油、毒素和宿便开始被分解、软化。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">～</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">小时内会无比通畅的排出松软成型的黑色油便、宿便和毒素，味臭，便量比平时大</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">倍，水面漂浮油花。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;排毒：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天净化体内，亮肤祛斑。燃脂梅作用的靶点在肠道，它不影响小肠的营养吸收，同时由于作用在大肠，可以阻止食物残渣里的脂肪、毒素在大肠的二次吸收。通过促进肠道的蠕动，可以快速排出，保持肠道的清洁和人体的健康。体内清洁自然原先松弛、起皱、色斑、虚弱、脸色蜡黄的皮肤变的红润有光泽。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;排油：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天纤腰收腹，减重控重。燃脂梅将中医排毒﹑减脂的原理和天然草本功能有机结合。通过调节人体脂肪的代谢机能，将聚集于体内多余的脂肪排出，同是有效阻止新摄入的脂肪在体内聚集。由于燃脂梅对脂肪的分解代谢能力强，因而腰﹑腹﹑臀部脂肪的转化与减少最为明显。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">燃脂梅</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">在减肥的同时，更注重五脏六腑的调理平衡，真正达到科学健康减肥的目的：&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\" class=\"15\"><span style=\"color:#e30151;\">1&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">调理肠腑，打通肠道，消除便秘、腹胀、腹泻、使蕴积体内的毒素顺利排出体外；&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\" class=\"15\"><span style=\"color:#e30151;\">2&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">调和气血，益气活血，快速消除脸上的暗疮、色斑，再现脸色红润光泽、皮肤细腻光滑，同时具有香身功效，让你遍体留香；&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\" class=\"15\"><span style=\"color:#e30151;\">3&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">调理脾胃，消食导滞，消除口干、口臭、身困乏力，让你清新自然，精力充沛；&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family:\'ˎ̥\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\" class=\"15\"><span style=\"color:#e30151;\">4&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"