ew Roman\';\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">体内环保：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">此种功效是保持血液的弱碱性，使酸性体质转为健康的弱碱性体质，保持肠内细菌均衡、强化细胞、促进消化、加强对病原菌的抵抗力，藉体内整顿作用获得平衡状态。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">2</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">抗炎：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">也是一种体内环保的作用。所谓炎症是指细胞局部受伤、破坏，病原菌在此安家、成长而引发的发炎，实际上，酵素并无治疗能力，但是它能诱发、强化白血球对抗坏菌，并清除入侵的病菌与化脓物，给予细胞修复和再生的条件使其加速伤口愈合能力。不论何种疾病，最基本的治疗仍是依靠人体的自然愈力。即使是特效药、抗生素，也只能消灭病原菌，无法新生细胞。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">3</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">抗菌：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;f