INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('5837','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><br />\r\n产品简介</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\"><br />\r\n逛逛网是全国首个敢于保证假一赔十的网上商城，所有商品均从厂家直接代理，保证质量的同时又给消费者最低的价格。同时我们提出消费养老的理念，把消费者的消费返利转为养老基金，解决广大用户的养老难题。逛逛网总部现已具备完善的运营体系，先进的商业模式，具有持续盈利的能力。所有逛逛网城市子公司将完全复制总部运营模式，实现即刻上线立即盈利，免除投资者的后顾之忧。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\"><br />\r\n逛逛网</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\">消费养老是新近崛起的一种养老模式，其核心是消费者在购买企业的产品后，企业应该给予消费者一定的养老金回馈制度，在不影响企业运营和消费者日常消费的过程中，实现零成本，轻松积攒养老金。和传统的商业模式相比，消费养老模式下，一方面，消费者在购买商品的过程中总会得到一些超出预期的收益，对此持欢迎的态度；另一方面，供应商得到大规模的订单，不仅使得他们扩大了市场，而且由于产品是由他们直接供应给消费品，成本会大大降低。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\"><br />\r\n消费养老可以实现商品销售、电子商务和养老保险三者结合。这是一个创新，对大家的理念都是一种冲击，这对传统养老模式是重要的补充。</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">这种新型的消费和社会保障模式具有很多优势，具体表现为：</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\">1、企业会拥有大量来自消费者的订单而成为市场的强者，并且消费养老会为养老经费提供一个广阔的巨大资金来源，能在不增加消费者负担的情况下，逐步为消费者积攒一笔可观的养老资金，从而解决许多与养老有关的难题。</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\">2、该模式会促进消费者采取正规的消费形式而获得能进入自己养老金账号的范例，从而有利于规范税收，防止部分企业和商家偷税漏税。</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\">3、通过这种消费模式，每个人都有了一个固定的养老经费账号，非常有利于个人各种养老金的延续和累计，有利于养老金的流动管理。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\"><br />\r\n消费养老理念是一种</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\">&ldquo;个人消费&mdash;&mdash;企业返利转为投资&mdash;&mdash;消费者获得投资增值红利&mdash;&mdash;解决个人养老资金来源&rdquo;的新型链条模式，通过电子商务商业模式解决了养老金问题。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\"><br />\r\n由于网站商品全部都是签订代理协议，赚取代理差价，大部分商品的毛利润可达50%以上。当消费者累计消费满1万元时，提出</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\">1</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\">0%，即</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\">1</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\">000元投入网站设立的养老投资基金，经营网站交易数据，逛逛网帮消费者使用基金来投资网上热销商品，并进行滚动投资</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\">3-</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;\">5年后，消费者可获取相当于消费本金的投资回报。所获回报可用于网站购物或提现。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><br />\r\n产品卖点</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br />\r\n我们为你想得更多，做得更好</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><br />\r\n<img src=\"/file/upload/201705/19/141211221.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"453\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"/file/upload/201705/19/141218721.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"453\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"/file/upload/201705/19/141225101.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"453\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"/file/upload/201705/19/141232551.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"453\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"/file/upload/201705/19/141239991.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"453\" alt=\"\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>');
INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('5836','&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: center;\">产品简介</span>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \" 冬青黑体简体中文=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">天美本地通</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&mdash;&mdash;</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">为本地人做事的生活服务平台</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \" 冬青黑体简体中文=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">天美本地通在2014年7月成立于山西侯马，2015年5月，天美本地通正式上线并登陆山西省侯马市，为侯马消费者开启&ldquo;本地生活服务&rdquo;的移动互联网生活。截止2016年7月份，已开通县域城市30余家，服务于300万县域市民，提供生活类配送，海鲜蔬菜，鲜花水果，餐饮熟食，从下单到接单，到送达，仅需半小时。天美本地通在慢慢改变县域城市居民的生活方式。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \" 冬青黑体简体中文=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">而今，天美本地通在天津建立全国运营中心，在北京建立全国技术中心，这也就意味着，天美本地通成为了山西省内首个把县域O2O生活服务平台做到全国市场的平台。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 31px; font-family: \" 冬青黑体简体中文=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">产品卖点</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \" 冬青黑体简体中文=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">小投资大回报，将传统行业结合互联网，打造新的盈利模式！</span></p>\r\n<img src=\"/file/upload/201705/18/153308394873.jpg\" width=\"412\" height=\"608\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"/file/upload/201705/18/153315594873.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"550\" alt=\"\" />');
INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('5817','<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"/file/upload/201705/18/102203391.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"222\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px;\"><br />\r\nTDT（杭州）互联网机构，专注为中国企业提供互联网+转型的创新交易平台，它瞄准未来全球产业资源化、数据化分工趋势，为企业与各类专业服务人才（机构）搭建撮合交易平台。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px;\"><br />\r\n公司，是一家年轻、快乐、创新的互联网公司，公司专注互联网+智慧营销的企业整合应用，以重构中国企业传统营销模式、推动中国企业营销智慧化为使命，成为天下营销人的经纪人，打造中国最大的智慧营销平台，一声江湖令，十万营销军。目前主要运营智慧招商、智慧运营（大数据分析、</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px;\">智慧办公、智慧销管、智慧订单、社圈系统）、智慧推广（帮助企业以众包模式进行品牌、产品推广）三大平台。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 27px;\"><br />\r\n公司分别在杭州余杭区海创园建立了移动互联网技术研发基地，在拱墅区中国（杭州）智慧信息产业园建立了平台运营基地。公司创始团队来自中国领先的软件公司、</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 27px;\">知名畅销品公司、硅谷创业公司、阿里巴巴等，</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 27px;\">拥有极深的技术与营销背景，</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 27px;\">凭借独特的商业模式和优越的项目前景，已经获得创投机构的千万领投，并</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 27px;\">成为世界500强IBM的核心战略伙伴。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 27px;\"><br />\r\n公司自主搭建的营销大数据服务中心（</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: justify; text-indent: 27px;\">IaaS）、云计算公共平台（PaaS）、应用软件服务（SaaS），已成为全国同行的技术领先者，为企业提供全面、先进的云端数据服务及系统解决方案。</span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>');
